# Snapping/Window Tiling
Mod1 Left :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Left}
Mod1 Right :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 50% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Right}
Mod1 Up :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 100% 100%} {MoveTo 00 00 Up}
Mod1 Down :MacroCmd {ResizeTo 100% 50%} {MoveTo 00 00 Bottom}
Mod1 s :ToggleCmd {Maximize} {Restore}

Mod4 n :Minimize
Mod4 m :Deiconify
Mod4 d :ToggleCmd {ShowDesktop} {Restore}
Mod1 e :Exec rofi -show window
Control Mod1 l :Exec xscreensaver-command -lock
Print :Exec spectacle
